abstract = {This paper presents a modular digital twin framework for High-Performance Computing (HPC) centers, to enable the optimization of their energy efficiency. The framework combines a FIWARE-based IoT platform with a hybrid modeling approach. The methodology is demonstrated at a German HPC center, where the digital twin is able to predict the Power Usage Effectiveness with an error of less than 2.5 \% while also identifying several operational inefficiencies.},
